      "content": "wait, why'd you say \"most economists agree\" like it's a settled fact? i've been reading a lot about how tariffs can actually help rebuild the middle class and stop us from being too dependent on other countries. how can you say one side is \"generally correct\" when there's clearly a huge debate about the social impact of these policies?",
